data.description: WOW! PERFECT CONDITION!! inside and out. Great quiet location at the rear of the complex. Hardwood entry and hardwood kitchen. Updated kitchen including newer appliances and Miracle counters. Bronze hardware, designer paint and white colonist door throughout. 2 master suites upstairs with central laundry closet including Maytag washer/dryer. Full finished and insulated garage. Quiet patio stucco exterior and tiled roof. WOW!!
